nt|^z@3^b@2^^|cp|8|AT|^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|So bidding 3@C right away puts a lot more pressure on North. The idea in competitive bidding is to pressure your opponents when you can because they will often make incorrect decisions.|
